      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAY MY GRACE (3) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (19.63) at this track in a Maiden. Has first look at box 3 this time. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Capable of going well again. TORO NERO (2) is a Emma Boreland-trained newcomer by Collide out of Splitting Image with no trial form to work with. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. GO WALLY GO (1) freshened since a nice debut run when hitting the frame at Warrnambool over 390m (22.46). Has the inside draw this time. Meets a moderate line up and should do much better. ASTON BOREALIS (8) deserves plenty of thought over this journey.",
